   489	- Payment fields (populated in §5.4.4): confirmed total, currency, wallet address, tx ID (optional)
   490	
   491	**Duplicate item in cart:** If the same compound + form + vial size is added more than once, quantities are merged into one line item. Different vial sizes of the same compound are separate line items.
   492	
