    18	- **Benefits**: Immutable record of system state; easy to query for admin adherence monitoring; satisfies security requirements; provides data recovery path.
    19	- **Costs**: Database storage growth (mitigated by 90-day rolling purge); additional latency on writes to record the audit event.

